setInterval(() => {
  const mem = process.memoryUsage();
  console.log(`RSS: ${(mem.rss / 1e6).toFixed(1)}MB, Heap: ${(mem.heapUsed / 1e6).toFixed(1)}MB`);
}, 30000);
```

If heap grows monotonically across snapshots, compare two snapshots in DevTools using the "Comparison" view to see which objects are accumulating.

